    <section class="project-overview">
        <p>Bedrock Proxy Endpoint allows you to spin up your own custom OpenAI API server endpoint for AWS Bedrock LLM text inference. It makes it easy to use AWS Bedrock with existing OpenAI API compatible applications by providing a compatible proxy that handles all the format conversions.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="project-features">
        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>OpenAI API compatibility layer for AWS Bedrock</li>
            <li>Support for multiple Bedrock models</li>
            <li>Format conversion between OpenAI and Bedrock</li>
            <li>Easy integration with existing applications</li>
            <li>Customizable endpoint configuration</li>
            <li>Detailed error handling and logging</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

